{"tid":2186734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黎智英涉恐嚇東方日報記者 罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-09-03T07:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T08:48:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":119,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"a6462bd11966e730f3990afd75832c9e6aa414f6","tid":2186734,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"三年前維園六四晚會開始前，壹傳媒創辦人黎智英當眾指罵《東方日報》男記者，揚言「我實搞你」、「影X咗你相」，至今年被控刑事恐嚇罪。黎智英上月受審，裁判官鍾明新今午於西九龍裁判法院就案件裁決，裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/47P3CGTV6BGETFBTNMXXGGFGUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2F47P3CGTV6BGETFBTNMXXGGFGUI%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=a4248796\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2F47P3CGTV6BGETFBTNMXXGGFGUI%2F&h=93844fae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/47P3CGTV6BGETFBTNMXXGGFGUI/</a>"},{"pid":"1d4b83a9b09401643deb75542c77d9be77b7a4d6","tid":2186734,"uid":241804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:13:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55306104b22d5be944136d553d41495ed4b9e87c","tid":2186734,"uid":240362,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">裁判官裁決指，控方必須證明兩項控罪元素，才可裁定黎智英罪名成立，包括黎確實作出威嚇會使事主X身體受到傷害、以及黎有意圖使X受驚。法庭在審視證人證供時，不但會考慮其作供舉止和神態，還會仔細考量作供的內容是否合理、是否符合常理、以及內在可能性。裁判官引述案例，指本案的重點在於黎案發時向X所作出的言論，是否因受到挑釁而在盛怒下作出。<br />\n<br />\n官：案中男記者不誠實亦不可靠<br />\n<br />\n裁判官認為X不誠實亦不可靠，作供期間迴避及自我保護，尤其在盤問下更見明顯，對於簡單直接的問題亦多次迴避。至於X的精神狀態，裁判官質疑是否因黎的說話所致。X案發時「笑笑口」，他解釋心裡害怕，嘗試令黎冷靜；裁判官表示，同意某些情況下受驚的人或有此表現，但不接納X若剛剛受驚嚇會作出如此表現，尤其他後來向同事表示「唉，乜今日咁燥」。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"009add44f5a3022f57ea0f817f5f5cc7f6de6260","tid":2186734,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9760a045b97f66c9f32e91cb0992709492af975f","tid":2186734,"uid":28960,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">據了解，律政司檢控人員和外間資深大律師的法律意見均不建議起訴，惟去年9月律政司司長鄭若驊親頒「御旨」，分析有合理勝算，建議檢控。</span>"},{"pid":"2a277bbde9d8c703855943f25e0b0376ca5b5697","tid":2186734,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763650eaf27d91ae98167d1084dbcbe89d0843c3","tid":2186734,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e35edd4253cbc6eb34b5969da2b83129cc09d9","tid":2186734,"uid":127929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:14:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hs9aoNG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHs9aoNG.jpg&h=2d5e44a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"143fb8dcdf09bcd4703251be7bbe72214f830b2c","tid":2186734,"uid":174512,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:14:18.000Z","msg":"班狗閪恐嚇市民又唔告<br />\nOn9"},{"pid":"fb41997e8c441b63d4f87bec6bd950e80a273e87","tid":2186734,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T07:14:24.000Z